headline: Lennar Announces the Retirement of General Counsel Mark Sustana and Chief Operating Officer Fred Rothman and Welcomes Katherine Lee Martin as Chief Legal Officer
summary: Lennar Corporation (NYSE: LEN and LEN.B), one of the nation's leading homebuilders, today announced that Mark Sustana, General Counsel and Vice President, will retire from the company, effective September 2, 2025. He will be succeeded by Katherine Lee Martin, who joins Lennar on September 2 as Chief Legal Officer. Ms. Martin most recently served as Executive Vice President, General Counsel and Corporate Secretary at The Hertz Corporation.
